English: <color=red>Warning. Hull interior layer has been breached. Immediate evacuation advised.</color>

Italian.Translation: <color=red>Attenzione. Lo strato interno dello scafo è stato violato. Consigliata l'evacuazione immediata.</color>

German.Translation: <color=red>Warnung. Die innere Schicht des Rumpfes wurde durchbrochen. Empfehle sofortige Evakuierung.</color>

Spanish.Translation: <color=red>Advertencia. Se ha roto la capa interior del casco. Se recomienda la evacuación inmediata</color>.

Russian.Translation: <color=red>Внимание! Внутренний слой корпуса поврежден. Рекомендуется немедленная эвакуация.</color>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: <color=red>Aviso. Camada interior da couraça infringida. Evacuação imediata aconselhada.</color>

Polish.Translation: <color=red>Ostrzeżenie. Wewnętrzna warstwa kadłuba naruszona. Zalecana natychmiastowa ewakuacja.</color>

Korean.Translation: <color=red>경고. 선체 내부 층이 뚫렸습니다. 즉시 대피하시기 바랍니다.</color>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: <color=red>警告。艙體內層遭入侵。建議立即撤離。</color>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: <color=red>警告。舱体内层已被侵入。建议立即撤离。</color>
